{"hotelId": 55643364, "platform": "Agoda", "hotelName": "Wonderwall Ximending", "comment": {"isShowReviewResponse": false, "hotelReviewId": 947982006, "providerId": 332, "rating": 9.6, "checkInDateMonthAndYear": "April 2025", "encryptedReviewData": "fPAmQDcBxxzs/sqLZAItmA==", "formattedRating": "9.6", "formattedReviewDate": "April 10, 2025", "ratingText": "Exceptional", "responderName": "Wonderwall Ximending", "responseDateText": "", "responseTranslateSource": "en", "reviewComments": "Pros:\n-Great location. It's just a very short walk away from the main Ximending market areas (just cross the street), so it's convenient if you're planning to go around the block. There are also enough taxis to ride if you need to go to other locations. AND it's not within the market area which is good as it is quiet and can allow you to rest well after a long day.\n-Great service from the staff. Helpful. Just approach them for your needs. \n-Clean. They change the sheets daily. \n-Getting into the area with the rooms requires a hotel keycard so it's secure. CCTVs are also operational in the hallways.\n-The reception area is spacious, neat, quiet, and affords a space to have your coffee and do some work. \n-Bed is comfortable, clean, and new. TV works fine. Facilities are also neat. \n-Shampoo, conditioner, shower gels, tissues and small and big towels are available- and they are of good quality. Hot and cold water available. The Dyson hair dryer in the room is handy as well. \n-A steam iron and a baggage weight checker are available at the counter. \n-24h staff service. They even help with booking taxis. \n-Laundry facilities can be used for free- just schedule with them. \n-Free water, coffee, and biscuits. \n\nCons:\n-No bidet. No bidet. \n-The building itself is old downstairs, and there are old shops which might cause one to feel unsure about entering it. But the hotel itself is fine. \n-The entrances can get confusing as there are several. But once you find the elevator to the 9